    <h1>Identity Resolution</h1>
    <p class="description">The process of matching user data across devices and channels to build a <strong>single unified customer profile</strong>. Enables accurate attribution, personalisation, and smarter ad spend across the full customer journey.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
